    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good honest condition and ready to enjoy as a solid driver. It shows nicely overall, with a clean appearance inside and out, and it appears to have been maintained better than many of its peers. Buyers should still expect normal age-related wear and some minor cosmetic imperfections, but nothing that takes away from it being a presentable, usable, and enjoyable vehicle. A good choice for someone looking for an older car that is above average in condition without paying top-tier show-car money.",
