    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "$17,900 - Good value for someone looking for an affordable car that\u2019s still very usable and presentable, with the kind of normal wear you\u2019d expect from a fair-condition vehicle. It\u2019s not perfect, but it offers solid basic transportation and a chance to get into something at a reasonable price. A sensible buy for a practical owner who wants decent value without paying top-dollar.",
